Convert a NetFileModel instance into a NeatGenome{T} instance.

Type Parameter
T

Neural net numeric data type.

Parameters
model
NetFileModel

The NetFileModel instance to convert from.

metaNeatGenome
MetaNeatGenome<T>

A MetaNeatGenome{T} instance; required to construct a new MetaNeatGenome{T}.

genomeId
int

The ID to assign to the created genome instance.

throwIfActivationFnMismatch
bool

If true then an exception is thrown if the activation function defined on model does not match the one defined on metaNeatGenome.  If false, and there is a mismatch, then the activation defined on the MetaNeatGenome{T} is used.

Returns

A new instance of MetaNeatGenome{T}.
